(9, 'ONE PLACE BANER', 'Mittal One Place: A Retail Hub Under A Single Rooftop\r\n\r\nThe developers of Mittal Brothers have constructed an enormous retail centre for various organizations to allow setting up their business and develop manifold. Situated at a strategic location in Baner, Pune, Mittal One Place exemplifies the blend of innovation with technology.\r\n\r\nFrom intrinsic architectural dcor to providing various amenities and facilities, Mittal One Place Baner is drawing massive attraction of business entrepreneurs who are willing to take their business to new heights. It is like a hub of an office where retail space is planned to perfection for benefitting the retailers who are willing to set up an office here. The offices or shops here have diverse configurations suiting the need of the buyers.\r\n\r\nThe building is strategically designed with the lower ground floor, upper ground floor and the first-floor specifically allotted for retail shops. The rest of the floors are however designed for creating office space.\r\n\r\nMittal One Place Pune, therefore, aims at multiplying business with a local boost of excellence. With numerous office and retail store at one destination, there will be more sale of products, as office going people will take an interest in purchasing their necessities or luxuries from these retail hubs. Besides, with the opening of numerous office spaces, there will be a vacancy for newcomers which will further yield in business growth.\r\n\r\nEvery shop or office space at Mittal One place is designed using modern, sleek furniture with vitrified flooring. The offices are spacious enough with ample provision for entry of natural light and ventilation. Even the retail outlets are designed in a way that they can store all the necessary goods required by the customers. Apart from the intrinsic interiors, Mittal One Place mesmerizes the visitors with the lavish exterior dcor. Lush green landscape adorned with tall trees and vibrant colour flowers amplifies the beauty of the retail hub.\r\n\r\nThe visitors here are facilitated with large car parking space. The project is expected to give excellent returns over the next few years. The well-planned retail spaces are instrumental in the growth of businesses, which makes this project one of the most coveted in the area.\r\n\r\nThe multi-storeyed retail hub at Mittal One place having various configurations of shops and offices are available at an affordable range.\r\n\r\nThe shops having a sizes between carpet area of 506 Sq.ft - 760  sq. ft. costs Rs.70.55 Lakh* - 1.76 Crore*  Thus buying an office space or retail outlet in Mittal One Place can help in the development of business by manifold.', 'PLOT A S, 16, Pan Card Club Rd, Baner, Pune, Maharashtra 411045', 'PLOT A S, 16, Pan Card Club Rd, Baner, Pune, Maharashtra 411045', 4, 1, '123', '123', 'P52100019584', 1, '2ACRE', 'Covered Parking::Gated Security::Conference Room::Society Office::Youth Hub', '', '', 36, 'new_launch', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Best Seller', '2023-12-11 11:56:14', '2024-01-05 08:14:43', 1),
