(681, 'DELLA TOWNSHIP PUNE', 'Della Township, North Hinjewadi  Luxury Living Meets Experiential Hospitality\r\nDella Township Pune is a visionary, racecourse-themed luxury township in North Hinjewadi, brought to life by Della Resorts & Adventure in collaboration with Hiranandani Communities and Krisala Developers. Spread across 40 acres within a grand 105-acre master township, it blends world-class luxury living with curated lifestyle experiences.\r\n\r\nPrime Location\r\nSituated near Punes thriving IT hub, North Hinjewadi, Della Township offers seamless connectivity, making it ideal for both luxurious living and high-return investments.\r\n\r\nInspired Theme\r\nWith British colonial architecture and an 8-acre Racecourse & International Polo Club, the township redefines premium living, offering residents an exclusive, regal lifestyle.\r\nCollaborators: Developed by Della Resorts & Adventures, in a joint venture with Hiranandani Communities and Krisala Developers  part of a larger 105-acre integrated township.\r\nScale & Investment: Spanning 40 acres, with Della\'s portion estimated at 1,100 crore and initial-phase investment of around 500 crore. \r\nTimeline: Land acquisition and planning are underway. Phase 1 is set to launch in the next 3 months, resort and villa plots will be ready for possession early next year, with private residences aiming for end-2026 completion. \r\nPre-Launch Schedule: Pre-launch expected around mid-to-late 2025, with full project completion stretching into 2029. \r\nUnique Amenities & Layout\r\nA truly experiential project, this township offers:\r\nAn 8-acre racecourse with an international polo club\r\n128 private villa plots for custom builds (4,5005,000 sq ft)\r\n112 resort-style private residences (~1,850 sq ft)\r\nA luxury 5-star resort (300+ keys)\r\nVenues for weddings (9) and corporate events (12)\r\nAn extreme adventure park, golf course, wellness center, spa, and glamping facilities\r\nArchitectural design blending British colonial, organic, and contemporary styles\r\nHospitality-first model aiming for up to 9% ROI through monetization via stays, events, and rentals.\r\n\r\nPricing & Investment Potential\r\n\r\nProperty Type   \r\nPrivate Villa Plot\r\nApprox. Size-4500-5000 SQFT  Price  Rs.2.50cr Projected  monthly income  1.87Lakh      \r\n\r\nResort Residence-\r\nApprox Size- 1850 Sq ft    Offer Price Rs.3.25Cr Projected Monthly Income 2.50Lakh    \r\n\r\nAppartment (1-3BHK)\r\nPrice  54.99L-RS.1.15CR    ROI  9%\r\n\r\nWhy This Township Stands Out:\r\n\r\nDual Appeal: Ideal for both luxury living and investment, especially for HNWIs, NRIs, and hospitality-focused buyers.\r\nStrategic Location: Well-connectedclose to HW-48, Hinjewadi IT park, upcoming Ring Road, and major urban centers. \r\nLifestyle Experience: Offers more than homeshospitality, adventure, wellness, and events under one roof.', 'Krisala x, Hiranandani Township, North, Hinjawadi, Pune, Maharashtra 410506', '', 2, 1, '123', '123', 'COMINGSOON', 0, '15acres', 'Garden::Swimming Pool::Kids Play Area::Gym::Temple::Gated community::Yoga Hall::Herbal Garden::Clubhouse::Indoor Games::Fire fighting system::Solar Pods::Bar Area::Seating Lounge::Wi Fi Zone::Bowling Alley::Fitness Center::Creche::Spa sauna steam room::Carron::Poker::Snooker::Table Tennis::Gaint Chess::Rock Climbing Walk::Wellness area::Library::Mini Golf::Project certified by  IGBC::Ground level amenities::Rain Water Harvesting::Power Backup common area::Automatic Elevators::Ample car parking::Access Control System::Bonfire Place::Racecourse Township', '55LOnward ', '', 441, 'token_started', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 240, '40acres', '1', 'Rushikes Sawant', '8605670460', 'Best Seller', '2025-08-08 07:30:43', '2025-09-27 17:15:13', 1),
(682, 'Della Racecourse Pune', 'Della Racecourse Township  Luxury Residences in North Hinjewadi, Pune\r\nExperience unmatched luxury at Della Racecourse Township, Punes first racecourse-themed luxury township by Della Group, in partnership with Hiranandani Communities and Krisala Developers. Spanning 40 acres within a 105-acre master plan, this prestigious development combines equestrian elegance with resort-style living.\r\n\r\nProject Highlights\r\n8-acre racecourse & international polo club\r\n\r\nBritish colonial architecture with bespoke interiors\r\n\r\n300-key five-star luxury resort\r\n\r\nWedding & corporate venues, golf range, spa, adventure park\r\n\r\nPremium clubhouses, sports facilities & landscaped gardens\r\n\r\nConfiguration & Carpet Area\r\n3 BHK Luxury Residences  Carpet: 1,2001,400 sq. ft.\r\n\r\n4 BHK Luxury Residences  Carpet: 1,8002,100 sq. ft.\r\n\r\nVilla Plots  Plot Size: 4,5005,000 sq. ft.\r\n\r\n(Layouts designed for maximum space efficiency and natural light.)\r\n\r\nPrice Range\r\n3 BHK  Starting from 2.25 Cr*\r\n\r\n4 BHK  Starting from 3.50 Cr*\r\n\r\nVilla Plots  Starting from 4.50 Cr*\r\n\r\n(Prices subject to change; please confirm current rates.)\r\n\r\nLocation Advantages\r\nLocated in North Hinjewadi, Della Racecourse Township offers excellent connectivity to:\r\n\r\nHinjewadi IT Parks\r\n\r\nMumbaiBengaluru Highway & Pune Expressway\r\n\r\nUpcoming Pune Ring Road\r\n\r\nTop schools, hospitals & entertainment hubs\r\n\r\nWhy Invest?\r\nWith an estimated ROI up to 9%, premium lifestyle amenities, and a landmark location, Della Racecourse Township is not just a home  its an elite investment for the future.\r\n\r\nBook your residence today and secure your address at Punes most iconic township  where luxury meets legacy.', 'Krisala x, Hiranandani Township, North, Hinjawadi, Pune, Maharashtra 410506', '', 2, 1, '123', '123', 'COMINGSOON', 0, '15Acres', 'Garden::Swimming Pool::Kids Play Area::Gym::Community Hall::Temple::Gated communi